== 生理活性 ==
木犀草素是一种PDE4抑制剂、[[磷酸二酯酶|磷酸二酯酶]]抑制剂<ref>{{cite journal |author=Yu MC, Chen JH, Lai CY, Han CY, Ko WC |title=Luteolin, a non-selective competitive inhibitor of phosphodiesterases 1-5, displaced [3H]-rolipram from high-affinity rolipram binding sites and reversed xylazine/ketamine-induced anesthesia |journal=Eur. J. Pharmacol. |volume=627 |issue=1–3 |pages=269–75 |pmid=19853596 |doi=10.1016/j.ejphar.2009.10.031 |url=http://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0014-2999(09)00922-4 |date=February 2010 |access-date=2011-07-02 |archive-date=2020-07-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200725140226/https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0014-2999%2809%2900922-4 |dead-url=no }}</ref>和[[白细胞介素6|白细胞介素6]]抑制剂<ref name=Johnson2008>{{cite journal |doi=10.1073/pnas.0802865105 |url=http://www.pnas.org/cgi/content/abstract/105/21/7534 |journal=Proc. Natl. Acad. Sci. U.S.A. |title=Luteolin reduces IL-6 production in microglia by inhibiting JNK phosphorylation and activation of AP-1 |first3=RW |last3=Johnson |first2=KW |last2=Kelley |volume=105 |author=Johnson |issue=21 |pages=7534–9 |date=May 2008 |pmid=18490655 |pmc=2396685 |access-date=2011-07-02 |archive-date=2008-06-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080607053040/http://www.pnas.org/cgi/content/abstract/105/21/7534 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

其可显著逆转小鼠的[[甲苯噻嗪|甲苯噻嗪]]/[[氯胺酮|氯胺酮]]诱导麻醉。<ref name=pmid19853596>{{cite journal | pmid = 19853596 | year = 2010 | last1 = Yu | first1 = MC | last2 = Chen | first2 = JH | last3 = Lai | first3 = CY | last4 = Han | first4 = CY | last5 = Ko | first5 = WC | title = Luteolin, a non-selective competitive inhibitor of phosphodiesterases 1-5, displaced 3H-rolipram from high-affinity rolipram binding sites and reversed xylazine/ketamine-induced anesthesia | volume = 627 | issue = 1–3 | pages = 269–75 | doi = 10.1016/j.ejphar.2009.10.031 | journal = European journal of pharmacology}}</ref>

临床前研究表明，木犀草素可能具有的药理作用，包括[[生物氧化|抗氧化]]、[[炎症|抗炎]]、[[感染|抗菌]]和[[癌症|抗癌]]。初步研究发现，木犀草素能够抑制[[血管|血管]]新生诱导细胞凋亡，影响动物模型肿瘤的发展，降低肿瘤的生长速度，并提高某些抗癌药物对肿瘤细胞的[[细胞毒性|细胞毒性]]，这表明木犀草素可能是潜在的癌症化学预防药物和化疗药物。木犀草素生物活性的机制可能为调节ROS的水平，抑制[[拓扑异构酶Ⅰ|拓扑异构酶Ⅰ]]和[[拓扑异构酶Ⅱ|拓扑异构酶Ⅱ]]、降低[[NF-κB|NF-κB]]和[[AP-1转录因子|AP-1转录因子]]的活性，稳定[[p53|p53]]及抑制[[磷酸肌醇3-激酶|磷酸肌醇3-激酶]]、[[信号转导和转录激活子3|信号转导和转录激活子3]]（{{small|STAT3}}）、[[胰岛素样生长因子1受体|胰岛素样生长因子1受体]]（{{small|IGF1R}}）和[[人类表皮生长因子受体II|人类表皮生长因子受体II]]的活性。<ref>{{cite journal|author=López-Lázaro M.|title=Distribution and biological activities of the flavonoid luteolin|journal=Mini Rev Med Chem.|volume=9|issue=1|pages=31–59|url=https://www.bentham.org/mrmc/sample/mrmc9-1/0004N.pdf|pmid=19149659|doi=10.2174/138955709787001712|access-date=2011-07-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100616071831/http://bentham.org/mrmc/sample/mrmc9-1/0004N.pdf|archive-date=2010-06-16|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

